

Adjustment Pack Application (0x0B)

    This register contains the adjustment value for battery type to improve the RSOC precision.
    
    Figure 13 and Table 7 show typical values of APA according to the design capacities per 1 cell and battery type.

When some batteries are connected in parallel, the design capacity per 1 cell is applied to the table
The APA values of Type−04 and Type−05 are used for battery type that is specified in Table 8.
Please contact ON Semiconductor if you don’t satisfy the RSOC precision.

The deeper adjustment of APA may improve the accuracy.

Alarm Low RSOC (0x13)

	The ALARMB pin will be set low when the RSOC value falls below this value, 
	will be released from low when RSOC value rises than this vqalue.
	Set to Zero to disable.
    
    ALARMB 핀은 RSOC 값이 설정된 값 이하일때 LOW로 설정 될 것입니다. 




https://android.googlesource.com/kernel/tegra/+/android-tegra-flounder-3.10-lollipop-release/drivers/power/lc709203f_battery.c



echo "lc709203f 0x0b" > /sys/bus/i2c/devices/i2c-2/new_device


Smart LiB Gauge Battery Fuel Gauge LSI for 1-cell lithium-ion/Polymer (Li+)

FUNTION OF REGISTERS

Executive RSOC initialization with sampled maximum voltage when 0xAA55 is set.

세팅된다. 0xAA55 일때 
최고치와 함께

RSOC 초기화가 실행되다

#!/bin/sh

#echo "lc709203f 0x0b" > /sys/bus/i2c/devices/i2c-2/new_device


rm lc709203f.ko

sync

cp /mnt/nfs/laringoscope/lc709203f.ko .

sync

insmod /mnt/nfs/laringoscope/lc709203f.ko

i2cdetect -y 2

sleep 1

rmmod /mnt/nfs/laringoscope/lc709203f.ko

exit

#echo 102 > /sys/class/gpio/export      # PWR_BUTTON
#echo 103 > /sys/class/gpio/export      # PWR_HOLD


cat /sys/class/gpio/gpio102/value
cat /sys/class/gpio/gpio103/value


echo out > /sys/class/gpio/gpio103/direction
echo 1 > /sys/class/gpio/gpio103/value

cat /sys/class/gpio/gpio102/value
cat /sys/class/gpio/gpio103/value



sleep 1

udhcpc -i wlan0

./nfsmnt 3.70

export TSLIB_FBDEVICE=/dev/fb0
export TSLIB_TSDEVICE=/dev/input/event0

